  "title": "Prime Mover Driver / Class 4 Driver (Vehicle can be driven back) #80660",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Logistics/ Freight Forwarding</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Prime Mover Driver / Class 4 Driver (Vehicle can be driven back)</strong></li><li>Working Location: Island wide</li><li>Working Hours: 5.5 days (Mon–Fri 8.30am–5.30pm; Sat 8.30am–12.30pm)</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Basic + OT + Incentive + Bonus (Gross up to $4500)</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Transport cargo safely between port, yard, and customer sites.</li><li>Drive and handle 20ft/40ft containers/ISO tanks.</li><li>Follow job assignments and routing instructions from the Traffic Controller.</li><li>Ensure safe driving practices and compliance with road safety and company regulations.</li><li>Perform basic vehicle checks (fuel, tyres, lights, brakes, etc.) and report any defects.</li><li>Ensure proper securing of containers/ISO tanks before movement.</li><li>Handle delivery documents and obtain necessary signatures from customers.</li><li>Other adhoc duties assigned by supervisor</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Valid Class 4 driving licence.</li><li>At least 1 year of relevant experience.</li><li>Familiar with port/PSA procedures and local road routes.</li><li>Willing to work overtime when required</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#80660 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Rachael Lee | EA Reg No.: R2093131</p>",
